        <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">A data visualization which has input of a clustered data set and produces an output of a report graph which is capable of rendering data of this type.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000117>James Malone</obo:IAO_0000117>
